Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:04:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來要拍攝選拔會  你一直期待的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然要選拔我的妹妹  好難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全靠「天氣少女  小魔女嘉音」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉絲裡增加了好多小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去淋個浴吧  好孩子的夥伴也得注意身體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼  我也想參加嘉音妹妹的選拔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  之前要先通過資料篩選
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你看起來跟嘉音差不多大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差得遠了  我比她大大約三百歲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請拿好資料進去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是  沒有資料的人禁止進入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:05:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知如此就多請教一下神哥哥關於妹屬性了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…驅魂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請放手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  都說不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是沒有宿主的落單驅魂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許在尋找寄宿的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趕緊捉住它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(490.909,77.5758)\frz-10\1c000000\3cFFFFFF}藝人淋浴間\N無關人員禁止進入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好小！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用羽衣幫你蓋上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  我還以為驅魂寄宿到嘉音身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是嘉音…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼看  我都變成小孩子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦哦  艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接下來還有工作  還要參加妹妹選拔會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岡田小姐還吩咐過我要注意身體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忽然地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐突地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就變成小孩的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜一下  嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音的危機就交給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部交給我解決吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要問我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不幹  這回的目標是驅魂本體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不正是你擅長的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還想我幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我現在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正進行著一場不能輸的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音之所以會變小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常來說都是因為驅魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用你的驅魂探測器把它找出來  捉住它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捉住施法後的驅魂  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次換你來排隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  我來讓嘉音變回…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪裡了  嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(56.25,84.8485)\fs24.2424\1cE0CBFF\3c8F78BC}中川嘉音\N妹妹選拔會\N會場在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無意中就溜出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道嗎  這裡除了有關人員是不能進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有大人在身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟嘉音就像是一個模子裡出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的真的好像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為就是本人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  你是來參加妹妹選拔的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才穿成這樣  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  跟我一起過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶你過去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,參加我自己的妹妹選拔？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小妹妹你叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中川…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…真音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真音？連名字都這麼像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(347.727,60.6061)\fs24.2424\1cBEC6E4\3c0D88F0}中川嘉音\N妹妹選拔會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好豪華
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看  這根緞帶跟嘉音的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像嘉音啊  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩了  該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一模一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太驚人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…其實  我不像你們那麼可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有  那根緞帶也很適合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真像嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  我很喜歡嘉音  能聽你這麼說好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:11:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜歡  所以很期待今天能見到嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成這副模樣…該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音要出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能  我就在這裡啊  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  是嘉音
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼  為什麼我會在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音她真的會魔法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天氣少女  小魔女嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每週星期天  絕讚播放中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天一定是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子  以為我就是電視劇裡的那個小魔女嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是那麼閃閃動人  會魔法也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然時間表排得滿滿的  不過接下小魔女的工作實在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是現在這個狀況該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底會怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那女生是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有兩個嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請把手機電源關閉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驅魂探測器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手機請關閉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是手機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:13:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那邊那個嘉音整個就是一個假…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了  你不能進裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我進去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中川嘉音  妹妹選拔會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別審查員當然就是這位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在嘉音面前能不能好好說話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了  嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了  有兩個我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是假的  是驅魂變的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驅魂？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家有危險  我們去通知她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:14:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驅魂肯定是想裝成嘉音去找間隙最大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24.2424}（嘉音請評論）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪  她跟平時不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  接下來是小梢  有請
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了  假貨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  請不要被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子才是真正的嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊真材實料的嘉音你們都不放在眼裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不行的  艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在還是小孩的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有些能確實證明是我自己的證據的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,證據？  我的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算變成這樣  唯獨歌聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你有完沒完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的歌迷小妹妹們是為了見我才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要裝成我  讓她們傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:15:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24.2424\fnDFGMaruGothic-Lt}何も聞こえない  喧騒のなかで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩蓋一切聲息的喧囂之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我  小魔女嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這肯定是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也變成小孩子了  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希  歌迷小妹妹們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  不趕快去救她們的話事情就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可以這樣  那我該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱歌  嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候驅魂對嘉音的歌有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驅魂是負能量  用嘉音的歌的正能量去衝擊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該會變弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請嘉音用你的歌去把那壞東西打倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用歌去打倒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24.2424\fnDFGMaruGothic-Lt}何も聞こえない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩蓋一切聲息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  就算是在夢裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的歌迷必須由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變身成小魔女嘉音了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我絕對會把大家救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也得快點去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為在夢裡面所以能飛起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小魔女嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來做你對手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個壞東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的歌把你打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女生是嘉音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  加油啊  嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驅魂拘留
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了  嘉音  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願明日天晴…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒過來發現大家都睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部人都睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊  果然是夢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音果然會用魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平安無事抓住驅魂實在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來嘉音好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後不找神哥哥  找嘉音幫忙抓驅魂好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這驅魂好像有什麼不夠的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道還沒抓完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次輪到我變成小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中川嘉音妹妹選拔會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優勝者是小梢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.91,0:22:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜  小梢  今天開始作為我的妹妹多多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音我好開心
